# MDI-SAM:
MDI annotation platform [SAM1](https://github.com/facebookresearch/segment-anything) &  [SAM2](https://github.com/facebookresearch/segment-anything-2) real-time recognition server ‚ö° .
Current support:
- (1) üåü Real time annotation: multi-point annotation, single rectangle annotation
- (2) üî• Prompt with different positive and negative values
- (3) üê¨ the Whole Slide Image recognition

